# Android release 签名模板：
# 1. 复制本文件为 `android/release-signing.properties`
# 2. 把 keystore 放到仓库根目录 `release/`
# 3. 按实际环境填写绝对路径、别名和密码
# 4. 然后执行 `npm run build:release`

storeFile=/absolute/path/to/moni/release/moni-release.p12
storePassword=replace-with-store-password
keyAlias=replace-with-key-alias
keyPassword=replace-with-key-password
